    <!-----About us Content ----->
    <section class="about-us">
        <div class="container">
            <h1>ABOUT US</h1>
            <p>
                Nestled in the heart of Cebu, Petrosial Hotel is your gateway to luxury and convenience. Offering stylish accommodations and breathtaking city views, our hotel is perfectly situated for both business and leisure travelers. With easy access to key destinations, including transport hubs and commercial centers, we ensure a seamless stay for our guests.
            </p>
            <p>
                Our hotel features well-appointed rooms with modern amenities, state-of-the-art meeting spaces, and a grand ballroom designed for memorable gatherings. Take a refreshing dip in our serene pool, maintain your fitness routine at our fully equipped gym, or indulge in an exquisite dining experience at our signature restaurant, serving a delightful array of international and local cuisine.
            </p>
            <p>
                Built on a foundation of excellence, Petrosial Hotel stands as a landmark of comfort and sophistication, reflecting Cebu's dynamic growth while preserving its rich heritage. Whether you're visiting for business or leisure, we invite you to experience a stay like no other.
            </p>

            <h2>GETTING HERE</h2>
            <ul>
                <li><strong>By Plane:</strong> <em>From Manila to Cebu</em> – Approximately 1 hour and 10 minutes</li>
                <li><strong>By Vessel:</strong> <em>From Manila to Cebu</em> – Approximately 12-14 hours</li>
                <li><strong>By Car:</strong> <em>From Mactan Cebu International Airport</em> – Approximately 30-45 minutes</li>
            </ul>

            <p><strong>Standard Check-In Time:</strong> 02:00 PM</p>
            <p><strong>Standard Check-Out Time:</strong> 12:00 NN</p>
        </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Reviews and Feedback Section -->
    <section class="reviews-section">
        <div class="container">
            <h2>GUEST REVIEWS</h2>

            <!-- Display success message if review was submitted -->
            @if (TempData["SuccessMessage"] != null)
            {
                <div class="success-message">
                    <p>@TempData["SuccessMessage"]</p>
                </div>
            }

            <!-- Reviews container -->
            <div class="reviews-container">
                <!-- Sample reviews -->
                <div class="review-card">
                    <div class="review-header">
                        <div class="reviewer-info">
                            <h4>JAY MENDEZ</h4>
                            <p class="review-date">March 15, 2025</p>
                        </div>
                        <div class="rating">
                            <i class="fas fa-star"></i>
                            <i class="fas fa-star"></i>
                            <i class="fas fa-star"></i>
                            <i class="fas fa-star"></i>
                            <i class="fas fa-star"></i>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <p class="review-text">"Incredible stay at Petrosia Hotel! The room was spotless with stunning city views. Staff went above and beyond to make our anniversary special. Highly recommend the breakfast buffet!"</p>
                </div>

                <div class="review-card">
                    <div class="review-header">
                        <div class="reviewer-info">
                            <h4>JOHN PLANAS</h4>
                            <p class="review-date">February 22, 2025</p>
                        </div>
                        <div class="rating">
                            <i class="fas fa-star"></i>
                            <i class="fas fa-star"></i>
                            <i class="fas fa-star"></i>
                            <i class="fas fa-star"></i>
                            <i class="far fa-star"></i>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <p class="review-text">"Perfect location for both business and leisure. The Executive Suite was well worth the upgrade. Only minor issue was the slow WiFi during peak hours. Otherwise, excellent service and amenities."</p>
                </div>

                <div class="review-card">
                    <div class="review-header">
                        <div class="reviewer-info">
                            <h4>PEARL MONCEDA</h4>
                            <p class="review-date">April 3, 2025</p>
                        </div>
                        <div class="rating">
                            <i class="fas fa-star"></i>
                            <i class="fas fa-star"></i>
                            <i class="fas fa-star"></i>
                            <i class="fas fa-star"></i>
                            <i class="fas fa-star-half-alt"></i>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <p class="review-text">"The Deluxe Twin room exceeded our expectations! Immaculately clean with thoughtful details everywhere. The hotel staff remembered my birthday with a surprise cake. Will definitely return next year!"</p>
                </div>
            </div>

            <!-- Feedback form -->
            <div class="feedback-form">
                <h3>Share Your Experience</h3>
                <form id="reviewForm" action="@Url.Action("SubmitReview", "Home")" method="post">
                    <div class="form-group">
                        <label for="name">Your Name</label>
                        <input type="text" id="name" name="name" required>
                    </div>

                    <div class="form-group">
                        <label for="email">Email</label>
                        <input type="email" id="email" name="email" required>
                    </div>

                    <div class="form-group">
                        <label>Rating</label>
                        <div class="rating-select">
                            <i class="far fa-star" data-rating="1"></i>
                            <i class="far fa-star" data-rating="2"></i>
                            <i class="far fa-star" data-rating="3"></i>
                            <i class="far fa-star" data-rating="4"></i>
                            <i class="far fa-star" data-rating="5"></i>
                        </div>
                        <input type="hidden" id="rating" name="rating" value="0">
                    </div>

                    <div class="form-group">
                        <label for="review">Your Review</label>
                        <textarea id="review" name="review" rows="5" required></textarea>
                    </div>

                    <button type="submit" class="about-btn">Submit Review</button>
                </form>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

